<head>AMUSED</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">逗笑兒</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>DELIGHTING in what TYPICALLY CAUSES one to FEEL SYMPATHY AND TO SMILE.</p>
    </div>
